Touch example:
cmnd/DVES_B46629/Power1 => on/off/toggle
cmnd/DVES_B46629/Status1

Enable hold & double:
SetOption1 1
SetOption11 1
StateText3 DOUBLE
ButtonTopic touch

// mqtt
FullTopic %prefix%/DVES_B46629/
MqttClient DVES_B46629

mqtt msgs:
stat/DVES_B46629/POWER = ON
cmnd/DVES_B46629_CMD/POWER = HOLD
cmnd/DVES_B46629_CMD/POWER = DOUBLE


List of commands:
https://github.com/arendst/Sonoff-Tasmota/wiki/Commands